    <title>
      <ph props="autonumber">9-1.</ph> Required Sources</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>FAR Part 8 establishes priorities for using Government sources for supplies and services. CHs must make their purchases in accordance with the priorities set forth in FAR Part 8.</p>
        <p id="Toc101947091">Table 9-1: FAR Part 8 - Required Sources of Supplies and Services</p>
