                        <b>FAR 8.002</b> 
                     </p> 
                     <p> 
                        <b>Priorities for Use of Mandatory Sources</b> 
                     </p> 
                  </entry>
                        <entry> 
                     <p> 
                        <b>Supplies</b> 
                     </p> 
                     <p outputclass="List2">1. Inventories of the requiring agency</p> 
                     <p outputclass="List2">2. Excess from other agencies</p> 
                     <p outputclass="List2">3. Federal Prison Industries (UNICOR)</p> 
                     <p outputclass="List2">4. AbilityOne â€“ products on Procurement List</p> 
                     <p outputclass="List2">5. Wholesale supply sources, such as stock programs of GSA, DLA, and military inventory control points</p> 
